title: 't Wethoudertje
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Dutch, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Biologische snackbar offering some vegetarian and vegan suitable foods. Items with cheese are clearly marked. Uses organic produce, and rice oil for frying. "Kroket" is a Dutch meat specialty, which this restaurant imitates with their vegan kroket.
